data.description: Come see this cute, quaint, and charming just like new home that is move in ready. The open concept of this home makes it perfect for entertaining. The spacious kitchen is filled with ample counter space, including a breakfast bar with a beautiful view overlooking the great room and dining area. Step out onto the brick paver patio to enjoy the large backyard which is ideal for all your outdoor activities. This home is located just outside the Bayside Lakes community in SE Palm Bay, FL, and only a 5-minute drive to the Publix Shopping Center. An added bonus for this home is its proximity to the beaches, space center, Port Canaveral, and Orlando's theme parks.
